The paper focuses on visual explanation for deep metric learning, which involves learning representations for images. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the interpretation of the model, which suggests that it may fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The potential applications mentioned in the paper, cross-view pattern discovery and interactive retrieval, suggest that it may also belong to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
